comments: Vucevic (ORL) is already in Neto's (WAS) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Neto (WAS) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Fultz (ORL) on the perimeter.
Neto (WAS) is moving alongside Fultz's (ORL) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) makes marginal contact with Bryant (WAS) that occurs prior to the start of Bryant's upward shooting motion.
Ross (ORL) is already in Bryant's (WAS) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Bryant (WAS) places his hand momentarily on Vucevic's (ORL) hip before immediately removing his hand.
Vucevic (ORL) and Bryant (WAS) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Bryant (WAS) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Vucevic's (ORL) drive to the basket.
Bryant (WAS) moves forward into Vucevic's (ORL) space and delivers contact that affects Vucevic's SQBR.  This contact occurs prior to and causes any potential traveling violation by Vucevic.
Bryant (WAS) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Vucevic's (ORL) shot attempt.
Neto (WAS) is moving alongside Fultz's (ORL) path and maintains a legal guarding position.
Bertans (WAS) is already in Fultz's (ORL) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Bertans (WAS) is already in Carter-Williams' (ORL) path when contact occurs and he absorbs the contact.
RAR shows Bryant (WAS) establishes a wide screening position in Carter-Williams' (ORL) path and contact occurs to his leg.
Fournier (ORL) moves to the side of Bertans (WAS) contesting his jump shot attempt and Bertans creates the marginal contact by extending his leg.
Bryant (WAS) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Vucevic (ORL) in the post.
Bryant (WAS) legally contests Vucevic's (ORL) shot near the rim.
Vucevic (ORL) is moving alongside Beal's (WAS) path to the basket and he legally contests Beal's driving shot attempt.
Brown Jr. (WAS) commits a take foul on Fournier (ORL).
Bryant (WAS) is already in Carter-Williams' (ORL) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Beal's (WAS) natural follow through causes him to move forward towards Vucevic (ORL) when contact occurs.
Brown Jr. (WAS) commits a take foul on Bacon (ORL).
Fultz (ORL) makes incidental contact with Neto (WAS) as he cleanly steals the ball.
Bertans (WAS) commits a take foul on Fultz (ORL).
